134, 125.2455, 125.7923, 125.3648, 125.4985, 125.3396, 125.174, 126.2192, 126.0597, 126.0353, 126.2885, 127.056, 127.7536, 128.2914, 128.627, 127.3469, 126.7126, 127.8348, 129.0854, 128.3074, 128.3407, 128.5574, 127.5411, 128.7897, 128.4818, 128.1152, 126.8545, 127.725, 128.0035, 128.2294, 129.1885, 129.9297, 129.8957, 131.5276, 132.686, 133.0595, 132.2927, 131.82, 132.3926, 132.1436, 132.3122, 132.5821, 131.8407, 131.697, 131.8159, 131.0619, 131.4211, 131.5663, 131.801, 132.0324, 132.6677, 132.6415, 131.6525, 131.7466, 132.1316, 131.6407, 132.3403, 132.6228, 132.9155, 133.5996, 133.3436, 133.4308, 133.8188, 135.3097, 134.2225, 133.8448, 133.8908, 134.9765, 135.2391, 134.8519, 135.1671, 135.8689, 135.7583, 136.1712, 136.0496, 136.932, 136.0916, 136.2052, 138.4881, 140.0331, 140.7608, 140.7161, 139.9908, 141.2604, 141.3246, 142.7273, 144.1828, 145.0324, 144.2309, 145.1739, 145.5293, 143.6634, 143.6657, 143.0157, 145.6216, 147.6807, 145.7648, 144.1558, 146.7699, 150.7188, 151.7373, 153.071, 153.4647, 150.1115, 151.6505, 154.5566, 154.7849, 152.8559, 154.4822, 156.2132, 158.8341, 158.385, 159.9464, 153.6383, 149.4835, 152.0215, 153.1846, 149.3054, 150.4412, 150.829, 150.9449, 152.8824, 151.6651, 152.6886, 153.2046, 154.0957, 153.0018, 154.2862, 155.1028, 150.5681, 153.3089, 151.9899, 148.9561, 151.388, 151.0293, 149.7277, 152.1906, 149.1951, 150.8567, 150.1379, 151.1482, 148.5625, 148.166, 144.9653, 145.9233], "summary_html": "<h1>不同频率视角下的选期因子 -- 通过 (Sharpe 1.11)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本策略复现了中信期货期货多因子系列第五篇中的三个截面选期因子：量价相关性、趋势强度和振幅偏离度。原文使用5分钟高频数据构建前两个因子，我们将其适配为日频数据版本。核心逻辑是：量价相关性反映了品种价格与成交量的共同运动方向，趋势强度衡量了价格位移与路程之比（即效率比率），振幅偏离度捕捉了高价区间与低价区间振幅的不对称性。三因子等权组合后截面排名，做多排名高的品种、做空排名低的品种，实现跨品种alpha捕获。</p>\n<p>最优变体是三因子等权组合(combo3_K5_raw)，Sharpe达到1.11，显著优于任何单因子。关键发现是量价相关性因子在日频数据上需要翻转方向（做空高相关、做多低相关），这与原文5分钟版本的方向相反，可能因为日频和分钟频率下量价关系的含义不同。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.78</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>5.1%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>6.4%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-9.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.08</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.06</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.51</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.94 / 1.17</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.8</span></td><td>0.95</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.48</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.02</span></td><td>1.15</td><td>0.89</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.18</span></td><td>1.52</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.5</span></td><td>1.62</td><td>0.8</td><td>0.57</td><td>1.41</td><td>0.33</td><td>0.56</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>open</code></td><td>开盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>volume</code></td><td>成交量</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每日</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>99.4%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>39.5</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<h3>Factor 1: 量价相关性 (Volume-Price Correlation)</h3>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Corr\\_VP}_t = -\\text{corr}(\\text{volume}_{[t-J,t]}, \\text{ret}_{[t-J,t]})</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{ret}_t = \\text{close}_t / \\text{close}_{t-1} - 1</span>，<span class=\"math-tex\">J=63</span> 日回看期。注意方向翻转（取负号）。</p>\n<h3>Factor 2: 趋势强度 (Trend Strength / Signed Efficiency Ratio)</h3>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Trend\\_STR}_t = \\frac{\\text{close}_t - \\text{close}_{t-J}}{\\sum_{i=1}^{J} |\\text{close}_i - \\text{close}_{i-1}|}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">J=243</span> 日。分子为有符号净位移，分母为绝对路程总长。值域 <span class=\"math-tex\">[-1, 1]</span>，接近 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\pm 1</span> 表示强趋势。</p>\n<h3>Factor 3: 振幅偏离度 (Bias Amplitude)</h3>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Amp}_i = \\frac{\\text{open}_i}{\\text{close}_i} - 1</div>\n<p>在回看期 <span class=\"math-tex\">J=63</span> 日内，按收盘价排序分为高价组（&gt;75%分位）和低价组（&lt;25%分位）：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Bias\\_Amp}_t = \\overline{\\text{Amp}^{\\text{upper}}}_t - \\overline{\\text{Amp}^{\\text{lower}}}_t</div>\n<p>方向：做空高Bias_Amp（高波动），做多低Bias_Amp（低波动效应）。</p>\n<h3>组合信号</h3>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_t = \\frac{1}{3}\\left(\\text{rank}(\\text{Corr\\_VP}_t^{\\text{neg}}) + \\text{rank}(\\text{Trend\\_STR}_t) + \\text{rank}(-\\text{Bias\\_Amp}_t)\\right)</div>\n<p>每个因子先截面百分位排名 <span class=\"math-tex\">[0,1]</span>，等权平均后再映射到连续信号 <span class=\"math-tex\">[-1, +1]</span>。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>corr_vp全部负Sharpe(-0.3~-1.1)，trend_str和bias_amp有正信号但不足0.8</td><td>1. 翻转corr_vp方向（取负号）2. 扩展hold_days到10-20降换手 3. 增加combo变体</td><td>Sharpe 0.68 -&gt; 0.88，corr_vp翻转后成为最强单因子(0.88)</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>通过(0.88)但未满3轮，combo可能更强</td><td>1. 聚焦最佳参数（corr:J=63, trend:J=243, amp:J=63）2. 增加vol_target_scale/IC gate变体 3. 三因子combo</td><td>Sharpe 0.88 -&gt; 1.11，<strong>combo3(三因子组合)成为最优</strong>，单因子互补效果显著</td></tr><tr><td>R3+</td><td>1.11已达标且超3轮</td><td>维持最优配置</td><td>decision=skip</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折点</strong>: R1发现corr_vp方向需翻转是全局最重要的改进（日频与分钟频率下量价关系含义不同）。R2发现三因子组合显著优于任何单因子（Sharpe从单因子最高0.88提升到组合1.11），验证了多因子互补的有效性。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频（原文Factor 1/2使用5min数据，已适配为日频proxy）</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全部商品期货（约57-80个活跃品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 5日调仓（最优），3-15日均有效</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 量价相关性因子在日频下方向与原文5分钟版本相反\n<p>- 振幅因子使用map_groups计算较慢（numpy循环） - combo3_K5_cs版本虽Sharpe也达1.0，但波动和回撤远大于raw版本 - 2021年和2023年个别年份Sharpe为负（宏观冲击期）</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9657</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 24.29s</li>\n</ul>"}